column5: Well as cold and windy as it was today, a good number of ice anglers were out. Close to 100 fish were caught if I remember correctly. My wife and I didn't have much luck finding any today in our usual spots but some did ok. The Mrs. ended up catching one of the freebie hats they threw out to the crowd. We didn't win anything in the draws either but the sausage was good....MMM.
